varCPParentBP — temporary storage for the current CP's Parent BP Identifier during Loop CP Rows iteration. String. Empty.
varCPOwningBU — temporary storage for the resolved BU lookup (or empty). String. Empty.
varCPResolved — counter — CPs whose BU was successfully derived (any of: BU-owned-inherited, Horizontal, Unresolved-BP, Missing-BP — i.e., the write happened). Integer. 0.
varCPInheritedBU — counter — CPs where Ownership Type was BU-owned and Target BU was inherited. Integer. 0.
varCPHorizontal — counter — CPs where Ownership Type was Horizontal (BU written as NULL). Integer. 0.
varCPUnresolvedBP — counter — CPs where the BP-to-BU mapping row was Status=Unresolved (BP awaiting classification). Integer. 0.
varCPMissingMapping — counter — CPs where no active mapping row existed (no row at all, or row was Ignored/Inactive). Integer. 0.
varCPManualSkipped — counter — CPs whose Manual Override (pei_owningbumanual = Yes) caused the write to be skipped. Integer. 0.
